27:33.109 --> 27:35.528
♪ From our mothers' arms ♪

27:35.612 --> 27:38.657
♪ Has blessed us on our way ♪

27:38.740 --> 27:41.159
♪ With countless gifts of love ♪

27:41.242 --> 27:44.913
♪ And still is ours today ♪

27:44.996 --> 27:47.415
♪ Of this world and the next ♪

27:48.124 --> 27:50.293
